ke přepruwowanje wotpopadnył.','Akismet was unable to check this comment (response: %s) but will automatically retry later.'=>'Akismet njemóžeše tutón komentar kontrolować (wotmołwa: %s), ale spyta pozdźišo hišće raz.','Please check your <a href="%s">Akismet configuration</a> and contact your web host if problems persist.'=>'Prošu přepruwujće <a href="%s">konfiguraciju Akismet</a> a stajće so ze swojim webhosćićelom do zwiska, jeli problemy dale traje.','Please <a href="%1$s">upgrade WordPress</a> to a current version, or <a href="%2$s">downgrade to version 2.4 of the Akismet plugin</a>.'=>'Prošu <a href="%1$s">aktualizujće WordPress</a> na aktualnu wersiju abo <a href="%2$s">wužiwajće staršu wersiju 2.4 tykača Akismet</a>.','Silently discard the worst and most pervasive spam so I never see it.'=>'Najhubjeńši a daloko rozšěrjeny spam skradźu zaćisnyć, zo njebych jón ženje widźał.','Some comments have not yet been checked for spam by Akismet. They have been temporarily held for moderation and will automatically be rechecked later.'=>'Někotre komentary njejsu so přez Akismet za spamom přepruwowali. Podleža nachwilu moderaciji a budźe so pozdźišo awtomatisce kontrolować.','Your firewall may be blocking Akismet from connecting to its API. Please contact your host and refer to <a href="%s" target="_blank">our guide about firewalls</a>.'=>'Waše wohnjomurja móhła Akismet při zwjazowanju z jeho API haćić. Prošu stajće so ze swojim hosćićelom do zwiska a hladajće do <a href="%s" target="_blank">našeho přewodnika wo wohnjomurjach</a>.','You can help us fight spam and upgrade your account by <a href="%s" target="_blank">contributing a token amount</a>.'=>'Móžeće nam pomhać, přećiwo spamej wojować a waše konto aktualizować, <a href="%s" target="_blank">darće za to symbolisku sumu</a>. ','Your web host or server administrator has disabled PHP&#8217;s <code>gethostbynamel</code> function.  <strong>Akismet cannot work correctly until this is fixed.</strong>  Please contact your we